query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q tq s) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 5
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('es')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('angularjs',
'array',
'asp.net',
'base-de-datos',
'c',
'css3',
'django',
'json',
'laravel-5',
'mysqli',
'nodejs',
'sql-server',
'vb.net');
